Dr. Abubakar Jimoh, Director of Public Affairs of the National Agency for Food and Drug Administration and Control (NAFDAC) was in the team of childhood friends who presented a congratulatory card to Vice President-elect Kashim Shettima on weekend in Abuja. Also, among the team was Dr. Salma Anas, a public health specialist and former commissioner for health with the Borno State Government; Dr. Jerry Cunningham, an American Agriculturist and Dr. Safiya Musa, a former staff of First Bank. Others who joined Dr. Jimoh in the courtesy visit to the Vice President-elect, Shettima were ACP Zakari Biu and Hajiya Maimuna Aliyu, former Executive Director of Aso Savings Bank among other dignitaries.